{"tid":115941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"終於同左男神告白","createTime":"2017-02-11T03:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T13:16:40.000Z","uid":77251,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caf9b535baacf990e9e7662eb51fc9e94d73c4ed","tid":115941,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"其實知道佢唔鍾意我<br />\n但係拖拖拉拉實在太辛苦<br />\n佢又一直欲拒還迎咁<br />\n結果尋日終於喺巴士站同佢講咗我鍾意佢<br />\n好樣衰咁大個女都係第一次告白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢話想做住朋友先<br />\n我嗰一刻真係覺得自己好柒好想搵個窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然一直同自己做左好多情境訓練 模擬比佢拒絕<br />\n但原來發生個一刻都真係會唔開心<br />\n雖然我會唔開心會喊但係我好慶幸終成件事於結束了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家情人節都有個伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1acc011504e44214b57c734f34310e601997265","tid":115941,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"做情境訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估走火演集呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ef190208f5acb83faeb0a1f0efaedd6adf02a2","tid":115941,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做情境訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估走火演集呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺個腦海度不斷地練習ff囉<br />\n等自己冇咁驚<br />\n點知都係冇用到期時驚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma